          <h1 class="h3 fw-bold mb-0">About ApolloNews</h1>
          <p class="text-muted small mb-0">Last updated: January 2025</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-content">
        <p class="lead">ApolloNews is an independent digital news aggregation and publishing platform dedicated to delivering fast, accurate, and impartial news to readers across India and the world.</p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Our Mission</h4>
        <p>In an age of information overload, ApolloNews exists to cut through the noise. Our mission is simple: to bring you credible, up-to-date news across every category that matters — technology, business, sports, entertainment, health, and science — without sensationalism, without bias, and without compromise.</p>
        <p>We believe that an informed citizen is the foundation of a functioning democracy, and we take that responsibility seriously.</p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">What We Do</h4>
        <p>ApolloNews automatically aggregates top news stories from reputable, licensed news sources worldwide, refreshing our database every 10 minutes. Every article links directly to its original source, ensuring full transparency and giving appropriate credit to the journalists and organisations who produced the original reporting.</p>
        <p>In addition to aggregated news, our editorial team publishes original in-depth blog articles on topics spanning technology, health, business, science, and Indian affairs.</p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Our Editorial Standards</h4>
        <p>ApolloNews adheres to the following principles in all editorial decisions:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Accuracy</strong> — We only surface news from established, reputable sources. We do not fabricate, distort, or misrepresent information.</li>
          <li><strong>Independence</strong> — Our editorial choices are not influenced by advertisers, political parties, or commercial interests.</li>
          <li><strong>Transparency</strong> — Every aggregated article links to its original source. Sponsored or promotional content is clearly labelled.</li>
          <li><strong>Fairness</strong> — We aim to represent multiple perspectives on complex issues and avoid partisan framing.</li>
          <li><strong>Accountability</strong> — When errors occur, we correct them promptly and prominently. See our <a href="/corrections">Corrections Policy</a>.</li>
        </ul>

        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">The Team</h4>
        <p>ApolloNews is built and maintained by a small, independent team of developers and journalists passionate about technology and public information. We are not affiliated with any political party, government body, or large media conglomerate.</p>

        <h4 class="fw-bold mt-4">Contact &amp; Feedback</h4>
        <p>We welcome feedback, corrections, partnership enquiries, and press outreach. Please visit our <a href="/contact">Contact page</a> to reach us.</p>
        <p>For advertising and sponsored content enquiries, see our <a href="/advertise">Advertise With Us</a> page.</p>

